title: #296: Brandon Goldberg, Stripper At Law (@AaronBergComedy)
itunes:title: Brandon Goldberg, Stripper At Law with Aaron Berg
description: Aaron Berg came to my apartment to tell me about his days as a male stripper in Toronto. It was really fun and got kind of seriously dark in the middle there. And then back to more fun. Come on along.
